_:N25a40c58b83d4e8c827b7d27c7da731e <http://schema.org/description> "This accessibility statement applies to documents published by the Government Analysis Function for England and Wales." .
_:N2236edf44cc04ab08907b7d8674ab98c <http://schema.org/name> "GOV.UK" .
